[31m-## 🚀 Overview[m
[31m-VXNEO is an automated platform that helps individuals opt out from data broker websites. It uses web automation to submit removal requests on your behalf, saving you hours of manual work.[m
[32m+[m[32m> Open-source privacy audit platform for detecting data breaches, broker exposures, and calculating comprehensive privacy scores.[m
 [m
 ## ✨ Features[m
[31m-- **Automated Opt-Out**: Submits requests to multiple data brokers automatically[m
[31m-- **Modern Stack**: Built with SvelteKit, TailwindCSS, and Playwright[m
[31m-- **Secure Authentication**: Magic link login via Supabase[m
[31m-- **Proxy Rotation**: Built-in proxy support to avoid detection[m
[31m-- **CAPTCHA Handling**: Integrated CAPTCHA solving capabilities[m
[31m-- **Real-time Dashboard**: Monitor your opt-out progress[m
[31m-- **Production Ready**: PM2 cluster mode, logging, and monitoring[m
[31m-- **Docker Support**: Easy containerized deployment[m
[31m-[m
[31m-## 🏗️ Architecture[m
[31m-┌─────────────┐ ┌─────────────┐ ┌─────────────┐[m
[31m-│ Frontend │───▶│ API │───▶│ Scraper │[m
[31m-│ (SvelteKit)│ │ (Node.js) │ │ (Playwright)│[m
[31m-└─────────────┘ └─────────────┘ └─────────────┘[m
[31m-│ │[m
[31m-┌──────▼──────┐ ┌─────▼──────┐[m
