[31m-text[m
[32m+[m[32m- 🔍 **Data Breach Detection** - Scan emails for compromised accounts via HIBP[m
[32m+[m[32m- 📊 **Privacy Score Calculation** - Get a comprehensive 0-100 privacy rating[m
[32m+[m[32m- 🎯 **Data Broker Tracking** - Identify where your personal data is being sold[m
[32m+[m[32m- 🤖 **Automated Processing** - Background workers process audits automatically[m
[32m+[m[32m- 🔐 **Secure Authentication** - Passwordless magic link authentication via Supabase[m
[32m+[m[32m- 📱 **Modern Dashboard** - Real-time privacy statistics, breach details, and recommendations[m
[32m+[m[32m- 🐳 **Docker Ready** - Complete containerized deployment with Docker Compose[m
 [m
[31m-## 🚦 Quick Start[m
[32m+[m[32m## 🚀 Quick Start[m
 [m
 ### Prerequisites[m
