[31m-- [Supabase account](https://supabase.com) (free tier)[m
[31m-- Git[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- Docker & Docker Compose[m
[32m+[m[32m- Node.js 20+ (for development)[m
[32m+[m[32m- Supabase account (free tier available)[m
[32m+[m[32m- Domain with SSL certificate (for production)[m
 [m
 ### Installation[m
 ```bash[m
 # Clone the repository[m
[31m-git clone https://github.com/yourusername/vxneo-hybrid.git[m
